CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 5, 1958, pg. B6 reads: "AMEZ Soiree Hostesses - AME Zion girls of the Pittsburgh District Churches, who were hostesses for the garden soiree, June 29, are, left to right: Jeanette Yarbrough, Carol Johnson, Phyllis Butler, Anne Sharp, Julia Diggs, Gloria Walker, Jacqueline Flowers, Betty Lee, Marcia Lee, Phyllis Carter, Shirley Perry, Shirley Lucas, Audrey Brooks, Gwendolyn Yarbrough and Janet White. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of AME Zion Church garden soiree hostesses, from left: Jeanette Yarbrough, Carol Johnson, Phyllis Butler, Anne Sharp, Julia Diggs, Gloria Walker, Jacqueline Flowers, Betty Lee, Marcia Lee, Phyllis Carter, Shirley Perry, Shirley Lucas, Audrey Brooks, Gwendolyn Yarbrough and Janet White, standing on lawn in front of brick building
